channel.title: Doesn't go past "loading please wait..."
channel.description:
Hey, my server now has some issues and it's not letting players log on... Like it won't go past the "Loading please wait..." part... And 1 of the players that mentioned that said that it might be because of the ::starter pack I recently added... But then it might be the silabs too since of all the new items...
Okay Edit: I tried it on my downloaded client and it works... it seems that it's just the webclient?

item.title: Doesn't go past "loading please wait..."
item.dc:creator: @eclipse245 eclipse245
item.description:
@eclipse245 wrote:

The account is “nulled” “Nulled” is the term we refer to when your account crashes, usually this happens with the SaveGames files which ar DATA files. So it is kind of irreversible. Best thing to do is just delete the file and start over.

Read full topic
